PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of PETER JOLLYMORE, of Saint John, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada for a term of three years, in the place of Hugh J. (Ted) Flemming, whose term has expired.
